DEVELOPMENT PLAN (DEVPLAN)

Standard Inspired: IEEE 1058 – Software Project Management Plan

1. Project Overview
1.1 Purpose

Define methods, tools, timeline, and responsibilities to develop Astra version 1.0.

1.2 Objectives

Deliver a complete RAG + ReAct reasoning engine.

Build a modern, high-impact UI.

Achieve local deployment with optional AWS integration.

2. Project Organization
2.1 Roles

Project Lead: You

AI/ML Developer: You

Frontend Developer: You

Backend Developer: You
(soloproyecto optimizado)

2.2 Tools

GitHub

FastAPI

LangChain

ChromaDB / FAISS

Next.js

TailwindCSS

Ollama (optional)

AWS S3/Lambda (optional)

3. Technical Process
3.1 Development Model

Hybrid Agile + Iterative refinement
Cycles:

Phase 1 — Core backend

Phase 2 — Core frontend

Phase 3 — RAG + ReAct

Phase 4 — Integrations

Phase 5 — UI/UX refinement

Phase 6 — Showcase build

4. Work Packages (WBS)
WP-01 Backend Foundations

Set up FastAPI

Document ingestion endpoint

Embedding generator

Vector DB persistence

WP-02 RAG Engine

Retriever implementation

Context builder

Chat endpoint

WP-03 ReAct Agent

Reasoning policies

Thought/Action/Observation pipeline

Output formatter

WP-04 Frontend

Dashboard

Chat + ReAct panel

Document viewer

Insights graphs

WP-05 Integration

API binding

Real-time UI updates

Error handling

WP-06 Deployment

Local docker deployment

Optional AWS serverless deployment
